{"id":"diblathaim","term":"Diblathaim","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Two cakes, a city of Moab, on the east of the Dead Sea (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 33:46\">Num. 33:46</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Jeremiah 48:22\">Jer. 48:22</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Numbers 33:46","Jeremiah 48:22"]}